7
00:00:22,010 --> 00:00:23,750
I'm never going back...

8
00:00:24,170 --> 00:00:27,200
I'll stay...forever...with you and the others...

9
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:28,940
Wait...

10
00:00:28,940 --> 00:00:29,860
Stop it!

11
00:00:31,290 --> 00:00:35,340
Think about it. This isn't where you belong, is it?

12
00:00:42,980 --> 00:00:44,690
Why...?

13
00:00:44,690 --> 00:00:46,310
Why...?

14
00:00:47,080 --> 00:00:48,490
Why...?

